President Obama has announced his intent to nominate three individuals to key Administration posts. Kevin F. O'Malley is nominated for Ambassador to Ireland at the Department of State. Jessie H. Roberson is nominated for Member of the Defense Nuclear Facilities Safety Board, and upon appointment, will be designated Vice Chair. Daniel J. Santos is nominated for Member of the Defense Nuclear Facilities Safety Board. These nominations are part of President Obama's efforts to bring talented individuals into his Administration.